    "instruction": "Load 'metric.csv' and 'trace.csv' from the current working directory. For each file, return a compact summary only: 1) total row count; 2) min(timestamp) and max(timestamp); 3) list of unique cmdb_id values; 4) list of unique kpi_name (for metric.csv) or trace_name (for trace.csv) up to 20 entries; 5) top 10 rows (head) as displayed by CSV reader. Do not print full time series. Keep outputs compact."
